# python3.12 [0], but can be substituted with setuptools. Pin below 82
# because setuptools>=82 drops pkg_resources, which is still imported by
# charms-reactive 1.5.3 (canonical/charms.reactive#263, fixed in PR #269).
#
# [0] https://docs.python.org/3.12/library/distutils.html
